      <section eId="sec_2404_D">
        <num>2404-D</num>
        <heading>Breast cancer; duty to provide extended hours</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_2404_D__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Monday through Friday, between the hours of 7:00 AM and 9:00 AM;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_2404_D__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Monday through Friday, between the hours of 5:00 PM and 7:00 PM;\nor\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_2404_D__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Saturday or Sunday, between the hours of 9:00 AM and 5:00 PM.\n  3. Waiver.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_2404_D__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>A facility may submit an application for a waiver from\nthe requirements of this section, in whole or in part, if it can\ndemonstrate, to the department's satisfaction, that the facility:\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_2404_D__subsec_i">
          <num>(i)</num>
          <content>
            <p>does not have sufficient staff to provide extended hours for\nscreening mammography services in accordance with this section, and that\nit is making diligent efforts to obtain staffing such that it can\nprovide extended hours;\n  (ii) is in the process of discontinuing screening mammography\nservices, as part of a consolidation or similar change; or\n  (iii) is subject to such other hardships as the department deems\nappropriate.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_2404_D__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The department may deny, grant or extend a waiver pursuant to\nparagraph</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_2404_D__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of this subdivision for ninety days, or more if the\ndepartment determines appropriate, in its sole discretion.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
